<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>HB00083</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : AN ACT INCREASING THE MINIMUM MONTHLY PENSION OF PRIVATE SECTOR PENSIONERS BY AMENDING SECTION 12 OF RA 11199, OTHERWISE KNOWN AS THE ꞌSOCIAL SECURITY ACT OF 2018ꞌ</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : Aims to increase the SSS minimum monthly pension of private sector pensioners from One thousand two hundred pesos (P1,200.00) to Three thousand two hundred pesos (P3,200.00) for members with at least ten (10) credited years of service and from Two thousand four hundred pesos (P2,400.00) to  Four thousand four hundred pesos (P4,400.00) for those with twenty (20) credited years of service, and shall be given in two tranches.</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>GARBIN, ALFREDO JR. A.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2019-07-01</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>CO-AUTHORS (Journal Entries) :</td></tr><tr><td>1. Salceda (000 2019-08-13)</td><td>2. Agabas (000 2019-10-02)</td><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT ENTERPRISES AND PRIVATIZATION ON 2019-07-23</td></tr></table>